title: Bug 114470[Smoke]Error message throws when using new Date("3/2/2005") as value in table filter.
description: Error message throws when using new Date("3/2/2005") as value in table filter.
OB: When using the value new Date("3/2/2005") in the table filter, an error message is thrown.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Open the application. 
2. Go to the table filter section. 
3. Enter the value new Date("3/2/2005") in the filter field. 
4. Press Enter or click on the filter button. 
5. Observe the error message thrown.
